# /src/ Directory Structure

The `/src/` directory contains the core source code for the AI Virtual Therapist project, including AI functionalities, blockchain integrations, and game SDK interactions.

## Directory Contents

```plaintext
/src/
├── ai_agent/             # AI core functionalities
│   ├── nlp/              # Natural Language Processing modules
│   ├── sentiment_analysis/ # Sentiment analysis logic
│   └── algorithms/       # Mathematical models and reusable AI logic
├── blockchain/           # Blockchain integration and smart contracts
│   ├── contracts/        # Smart contracts written in Solidity
│   ├── interactions/     # Blockchain interaction scripts
│   └── tests/            # Smart contract testing
├── game_sdk/             # Integration with Game SDK for AI interactions
│   ├── sdk_api/          # API calls to Game SDK
│   ├── agent_behaviors/  # AI agent behaviors within the game
│   └── utils/            # Helper functions for SDK integration
